## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="07f17-275">下列範例會使用合成，說出的片語預設音訊輸出。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07f17-275">The following example uses the synthesizer to speak a phrase to the default audio output.</span></span>  
  
